reviewText:
This game is like a cheaper version of Microsoft Outlook, only with less functionality - Having had too much to drink one night I mistakenly assumed the game's interface was my email client and attempted to email HMRC about my taxes.

Long story short, I'm now living out of the back of a Volvo with a person of unknown gender who smells mildly of soup mix and snores like a warthog.

10/10 this game started the adventure of a lifetime.
